Shared Tools and Utilities for Software Testing

This space provides a centralized location for tools and utilities developed and maintained by the Automation Testing team and shared across the Software Testing department.

The purpose of this page is to improve collaboration, promote reuse of existing solutions, and streamline testing workflows by making internally developed tools easily accessible to the entire team.

The tools listed here support various testing activities, such as:

Test automation support utilities

Data generation and test data management

Environment setup and configuration helpers

Reporting and analysis tools

CI/CD testing integrations

Debugging and troubleshooting utilities


By sharing these resources, we aim to reduce duplicated effort, improve testing efficiency, and enable teams to leverage proven solutions created within the organization.

Each tool entry should include a short description, usage instructions, repository location, and contact person or maintainer for support.


